Joyride (1997 - USA)

Comedy / Crime / Drama

starring . . . Tobey Maguire, Amy Hathaway, Wilson Cruz, Benicio Del Toro
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0119426/


In a half empty motel situated outside of a small town in Middle America, the only thrills are the kind that get you in trouble. One Friday evening, the motel owner's restless son (Tobey Maguire) talks his buddy (Wilson Cruz) into stealing a car for a late night spin. Anxious to escape from her pandering father, a young guest (Amy Hathaway) at the motel decides to go along - and the three of them set off for the ride of a lifetime. When they discover the dead body of a local doctor in the trunk, they wind up in a vicious battle of wits against the car's owner, a sexy assassin (Christina Naify). To make matters worse, a detective (Benicio Del Toro) starts snooping around in search of the killer. These offbeat characters turn a teenage prank into a desperate struggle for survival.
